  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<div class=\"spell-description\">\n  <p>\n    <strong>School</strong>&nbsp;divination;\n    <strong>Level</strong>&nbsp;psychic 8, sorcerer/wizard 8, witch 8;\n    \n    \n    \n    <strong>Bloodline</strong>&nbsp;Starsoul 8;\n  </p>\n  <p>\n    <strong>Casting Time</strong>&nbsp;1 minute<br>\n    <strong>Components</strong>&nbsp;V, S, M (a handful of crystal marbles)<br>\n  </p>\n  <p>\n    <strong>Range</strong>&nbsp;1 miles<br>\n    \n    \n    <strong>Effect</strong>&nbsp;10 or more levitating eyes<br>\n    <strong>Duration</strong>&nbsp;1 hour/level; see text<br>\n    <strong>Saving Throw</strong>&nbsp;none;&nbsp;<strong>Spell Resistance</strong>&nbsp;no<br>\n  </p>\n  <h2>Description</h2>\n  <p>This spell functions like <i>prying eyes,</i> except that the eyes can see all things as they actually are, just as if they had <i>true seeing</i> with a range of 120 feet. Thus, they can navigate darkened areas at normal speed. Also, a <i>greater prying eye</i>'s maximum Perception modifier is +25 instead of +15.</p>\n</div>\n",
